usage: make <command>

== commands

  console         Start an IRB session (alias: "c")
  install         Create .env file, install dependencies and run migrations
  test            Run all tests in tests folder (alias: "t")
  update          Install dependencies, includes development dependencies
  migrate         Run pending migrations
  migrate_testing Run migrations for testing database
  tdd             Run all tests with `watch -n0 ...`
  
  sequel -r ./app.rb -M 0 -m db/migrations/
  sequel -r ./tests/helper.rb -M 0 -m db/migrations/

